</span><br><br>Co-Founder &amp; Chief Winemaker</span></h3><p class="sc-hYQoXb koTnzq pf-117_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-119_">David has decades of experience, technical skill &amp; creativity. He is celebrated as the pioneer of modern winemaking in Portugal and is the only non-Portuguese national to win Winemaker of the Year – not once, but twice - in 2013 and 2015.
